{"prompt": "Generate a website for a AI startup. The website should be artistic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Nova AI</title>\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap');\n\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #8B0000; /* Dark Red */\n            --secondary-color: #A0522D; /* Sienna - a muted, warm secondary color */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #f8f8f8;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50%;\n            left: -50%;\n            width: 200%;\n            height: 200%;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 60%);\n            animation: pulse 5s infinite ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.05); opacity: 0.7; }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n            font-size: 4rem;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        h2::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 50%;\n            bottom: -10px;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            width: 60px;\n            height: 3px;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .subtitle {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto 40px auto;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            border: 2px solid var(--brand-color);\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .contact {\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .contact form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 15px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            max-width: 500px;\n            margin-left: auto;\n            margin-right: auto;\n        }\n\n        .contact input,\n        .contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .contact input:focus,\n        .contact textarea:focus {\n            outline: none;\n            border-color: var(--brand-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .contact .submit-button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact .submit-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        .nav-links {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 30px;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n\n        .nav-links a {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .nav-links a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .logo {\n            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            font-weight: 700;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            h1 {\n                font-size: 3rem;\n            }\n            h2 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n            .subtitle {\n                font-size: 1.2rem;\n            }\n            .nav-links {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                gap: 15px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"logo\">Nova AI</div>\n        <nav>\n            <ul class=\"nav-links\">\n                <li><a href=\"#features\">Features</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n        <h1>Innovating Tomorrow with Intelligent Solutions</h1>\n        <p class=\"subtitle\">Harnessing the power of Artificial Intelligence to unlock new possibilities and drive transformative change.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"features\">\n        <h2>Our Core Strengths</h2>\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Machine Learning</h3>\n                <p>Leveraging advanced algorithms to extract insights and automate complex tasks.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Natural Language Processing</h3>\n                <p>Enabling seamless human-computer interaction through sophisticated language understanding.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Computer Vision</h3>\n                <p>Empowering systems to perceive and interpret visual information with human-like accuracy.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Data Analytics</h3>\n                <p>Transforming raw data into actionable intelligence for strategic decision-making.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <h2>About Nova AI</h2>\n        <p style=\"max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;\">At Nova AI, we are a passionate team of researchers, engineers, and innovators dedicated to pushing the boundaries of artificial intelligence. Our mission is to create intelligent systems that are not only powerful and efficient but also ethical and beneficial to society. We believe in the transformative power of AI to solve some of the world's most pressing challenges.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n        <h2>Let's Build the Future Together</h2>\n        <p>Have a project in mind or want to learn more about our services?</p>\n        <form>\n            <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n            <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n            <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"6\" required></textarea>\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"submit-button\">Send Message</button>\n        </form>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Nova AI. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add subtle animations or interactivity if needed.\n        // For this artistic approach, minimal JS is preferred.\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}